00:31:13,380 --> 00:31:14,300
Start checking immediately

570
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:16,410
for any missing persons reports from bars or dance halls.

571
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:17,990
If there are none, we will start the investigation right away.

572
00:31:17,990 --> 00:31:18,600
Yes.

573
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:20,500
Wait a moment, Captain Zhang.

574
00:31:20,670 --> 00:31:22,790
We can hold off on the investigation for now.

575
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:25,040
Shanghai has thousands of dance halls.

576
00:31:25,080 --> 00:31:26,810
We can't investigate them all.

577
00:31:27,050 --> 00:31:28,980
I believe that three days from now,

578
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:30,150
the dancer's employer will come forward

579
00:31:30,150 --> 00:31:31,610
to report her missing.

580
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:34,640
Is that possible?

581
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:36,220
Doctor Jin just said

582
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:37,940
that the dancer was murdered yesterday.

583
00:31:37,940 --> 00:31:39,340
Looking at her attire,

584
00:31:39,370 --> 00:31:41,430
she must be a prominent dancer from the dance hall,

585
00:31:41,430 --> 00:31:43,580
commonly referred to as a "lead dancer."

586
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:45,880
It's normal for these lead dancers to be absent for a day or two

587
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:48,170
if they go out with clients.

588
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:49,990
If they're gone for three or four days,

589
00:31:49,990 --> 00:31:52,600
the employers will start looking for them through their own channels.

590
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:53,620
If they're still missing after five or six days,

591
00:31:53,620 --> 00:31:55,930
in other words, if they haven't returned by three days from now,

592
00:31:55,930 --> 00:31:58,200
then the employers will definitely come to report their missing.

593
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,640
After all, this dancer

594
00:31:59,670 --> 00:32:01,390
is their cash cow.

595
00:32:01,750 --> 00:32:03,390
Comrade Lin, you are very knowledgeable

596
00:32:03,390 --> 00:32:04,790
about the dance halls.

597
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,180
Director Lu, Captain Zhang,

598
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:09,580
I need to get back to work.

599
00:32:27,270 --> 00:32:28,110
Lin,

600
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:29,490
you are a Shanghai native, right?

601
00:32:29,490 --> 00:32:30,910
Yes, Captain Zhang.

602
00:32:31,790 --> 00:32:32,910
Our Criminal Police Division

603
00:32:32,910 --> 00:32:34,860
is lacking someone like you who understands Shanghai so well

604
00:32:34,860 --> 00:32:36,290
and is sharp-minded.

605
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:36,970
I think

606
00:32:36,990 --> 00:32:40,320
you would be more adept at investigating homicides than catching agents.

607
00:32:40,320 --> 00:32:42,650
Would you consider coming to work with me?

608
00:32:42,650 --> 00:32:44,000
Is that for real, Captain Zhang?

609
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:44,910
Yes, it is.

610
00:32:46,170 --> 00:32:47,850
If I join your department,

611
00:32:47,870 --> 00:32:49,710
could I be transferred from an auxiliary officer

612
00:32:49,710 --> 00:32:51,050
to a regular police officer?

613
00:32:51,050 --> 00:32:51,930
What?

614
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:53,850
You're still an auxiliary personnel?

615
00:32:53,850 --> 00:32:54,650
Yes.

616
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:57,440
A talent like you is still an auxiliary?

617
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:58,370
Here's the deal.

618
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:00,230
The hardships you endured in the Social Affairs Office

619
00:33:00,230 --> 00:33:01,350
will all be compensated for

620
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,830
in my Criminal Police Division.

621
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:03,650
Here,

622
00:33:03,670 --> 00:33:04,910
give me your data.

623
00:33:04,950 --> 00:33:06,000
Bring it over now.

624
00:33:06,020 --> 00:33:06,880
Captain Zhang.

625
00:33:07,500 --> 00:33:09,530
Comrade Lin won't be coming to your department.

626
00:33:09,530 --> 00:33:12,460
We also urgently need manpower for catching agents,

627
00:33:12,470 --> 00:33:14,040
right, Comrade Lin?

628
00:33:16,340 --> 00:33:17,060
Yes.

629
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:18,500
Director Lu is right.

630
00:33:19,870 --> 00:33:20,590
Lu,

631
00:33:20,620 --> 00:33:22,100
based on our relationship...

632
00:33:22,100 --> 00:33:23,400
What does our relationship have to do with this?

633
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,530
Right now, we are discussing the case.

634
00:33:26,410 --> 00:33:27,670
I understand the case.

635
00:33:27,670 --> 00:33:29,930
If there are any updates, let's communicate at any time.

636
00:33:29,930 --> 00:33:30,570
Let's go.

637
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:31,420
Lu.

638
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:32,620
Lu.

639
00:33:32,650 --> 00:33:33,320
Captain Zhang,

640
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:34,390
once this case is over,

641
00:33:34,390 --> 00:33:35,460
we can discuss it in detail.

642
00:33:35,460 --> 00:33:36,590
I'll be going ahead.

643
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,790
So petty.

644
00:33:41,630 --> 00:33:43,570
I'll find a day to bring him over.

645
00:33:47,450 --> 00:33:49,340
I discovered a truth today.

646
00:33:49,630 --> 00:33:52,560
Gold shines everywhere.

647
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:55,920
Did you shine before the liberation?

648
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,630
You thought Zhang really wanted you?

649
00:33:57,630 --> 00:33:58,640
What else?

650
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:01,650
It's because our department took Cen Xiaoman,

651
00:34:01,650 --> 00:34:03,110
and he's unhappy about it.

652
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:04,890
You, gold?

653
00:34:08,900 --> 00:34:09,690
By the way,

654
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:11,080
how much of your area

655
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:12,469
has been checked?

656
00:34:13,350 --> 00:34:15,090
About a quarter.

657
00:34:15,900 --> 00:34:17,150
Well, mainly the method

658
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,420
is really both clumsy and slow.

659
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:20,020
I want to go faster but can't.

660
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,790
When investigating a case,

661
00:34:21,790 --> 00:34:23,850
you can't always look for shortcuts.

662
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:26,460
It's necessary to investigate methodically.

663
00:34:27,219 --> 00:34:29,350
Sometimes slow is actually fast.

664
00:34:29,429 --> 00:34:30,239
Yes, yes, yes,

665
00:34:30,270 --> 00:34:33,130
you're the leader, and everything you say is right.

666
00:34:35,909 --> 00:34:37,020
Lu.

667
00:34:37,020 --> 00:34:38,080
what are you doing?

668
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,940
Mr. Jin, I'll return the money to you.

669
00:34:41,969 --> 00:34:43,760
Sorry, I missed it.

670
00:34:43,820 --> 00:34:45,219
The person wasn't found.

671
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,920
This person is not ordinary.

672
00:34:47,210 --> 00:34:50,150
His movements are secretive, and there are few clues.

673
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:52,550
Mr. Jiang, I didn't expect you, as a killer,

674
00:34:53,489 --> 00:34:55,120
to be so honest.

675
00:34:55,679 --> 00:34:57,680
Every profession has its own rules.

676
00:34:58,030 --> 00:34:59,880
I only take what I'm owed.

677
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:01,940
I prefer

678
00:35:02,830 --> 00:35:05,070
to cooperate with those who follow the rules.

679
00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:07,000
Returning the money is a bit early.

680
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:09,240
Our cooperation is not over yet.

681
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:12,890
Mr. Jin, do you have other methods?

682
00:35:13,440 --> 00:35:16,370
Once the arrow is released, there's no turning back.

683
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,470
Mr. Jiang,

684
00:35:17,870 --> 00:35:19,490
let me remind you again

685
00:35:19,990 --> 00:35:22,730
that this person is a senior Kuomintang agent.

686
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:24,360
He's sly and ruthless.

687
00:35:24,910 --> 00:35:27,040
You must not expose yourself

688
00:35:27,270 --> 00:35:28,210
or...

689
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:29,680
Rest assured, Mr. Jin,

690
00:35:29,990 --> 00:35:31,310
even if I die,

691
00:35:31,870 --> 00:35:33,290
I will never expose you.

692
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:35,330
That's also a rule.

693
00:35:39,900 --> 00:35:40,940
Wait for my news.

694
00:35:48,990 --> 00:35:49,810
Take a look.

695
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,350
Do you recognize this person?

696
00:35:52,350 --> 00:35:53,540
Have you seen this person?

697
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:54,400
Have you seen this person?

698
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:55,660
I really haven't seen her.

699
00:35:55,660 --> 00:35:57,310
I definitely haven't seen her.

700
00:35:57,310 --> 00:35:57,990
Alright.

701
00:35:58,300 --> 00:35:59,080
How's it going?

702
00:35:59,080 --> 00:36:00,000
Nothing was found.

703
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,060
Nothing was found.

704
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:05,110
Xiaoman.

705
00:36:08,270 --> 00:36:09,130
How's it going?

706
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:11,920
Can you hurry up?

707
00:36:11,950 --> 00:36:13,210
We're already behind.

708
00:36:13,210 --> 00:36:13,770
Well.

709
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,400
I was already very fast.

710
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:16,940
My legs are about to cramp.

711
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:18,710
Can you help me carry this?

712
00:36:18,710 --> 00:36:19,540
Why?

713
00:36:20,910 --> 00:36:22,290
I see you're tired too.

714
00:36:22,350 --> 00:36:24,080
I'll go buy two bottles of soda.

715
00:36:24,390 --> 00:36:25,190
I'm not tired.

716
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:26,350
Hurry up.

717
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:41,780
[Investigators: Xu Wei, Lin Shaobai]

718
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:44,520
Thank you, Officer Lin.

719
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:45,680
Yes.

720
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:47,500
If you hadn't insisted on helping us,

721
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:49,320
Wangju would have been sold to the Southeast Asia.

722
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,800
Yes, thank you very much.

723
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:52,180
It's good that she's been found now.

724
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:52,860
Wangju,

725
00:36:53,030 --> 00:36:54,630
quickly bow to Officer Lin.

726
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:55,420
Hurry up.

727
00:36:57,130 --> 00:36:58,460
Thank you, Officer Lin.

728
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,460
Sorry for my poor drawing.

729
00:37:37,540 --> 00:37:39,270
It's Zhao Wangju.

730
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:47,280
Our team has done the least checking.

731
00:37:47,310 --> 00:37:49,200
[Team check]

732
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:49,480
Lin Shaobai checked for a while and then said he was so thirsty

733
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:50,300
that he needed to go buy some water.

734
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:51,010
But he hasn't come back.

735
00:37:51,010 --> 00:37:53,050
Speaking ill of me again, Xiaoman?

736
00:37:56,350 --> 00:37:58,670
Director, I've found a clue.

737
00:37:58,850 --> 00:38:00,360
The one who killed Zhao Wangju

738
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,820
is very likely Wang Liqun.

739
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:03,390
Zhao Wangju?

740
00:38:03,490 --> 00:38:05,440
The first case I handled as a police officer

741
00:38:05,440 --> 00:38:07,590
was rescuing a group of trafficked girls.

742
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:09,230
Zhao Wangju was among them,

743
00:38:09,290 --> 00:38:10,370
the very dancer

744
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,980
who was just murdered.

745
00:38:13,630 --> 00:38:15,030
Do you remember our assumptions

746
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:16,490
about Wang Liqun's personality?

747
00:38:16,490 --> 00:38:17,660
He is ruthless,

748
00:38:17,700 --> 00:38:18,760
impulsive,

749
00:38:18,790 --> 00:38:19,650
and lustful.

750
00:38:19,670 --> 00:38:22,480
And the victim happened to be in Putuo.

751
00:38:23,110 --> 00:38:24,520
Based on these,

752
00:38:25,070 --> 00:38:27,470
you conclude that Wang Liqun is the killer?

753
00:38:27,540 --> 00:38:29,200
The possibility is very high.

754
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:31,860
This is just your conjecture.

755
00:38:31,860 --> 00:38:33,330
According to Li Qian's confession,

756
00:38:33,330 --> 00:38:34,580
we have basically confirmed

757
00:38:33,380 --> 00:38:35,850
[Arrangement]

758
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:36,050
Wang Liqun's activity range.

759
00:38:36,050 --> 00:38:37,470
As long as we continue the investigation,

760
00:38:37,470 --> 00:38:39,200
we will definitely find clues.

761
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:41,030
Diverting limited resources

762
00:38:41,030 --> 00:38:42,330
to investigate another case

763
00:38:42,330 --> 00:38:43,790
will only delay the progress.

764
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:45,100
Director, trust me.

765
00:38:45,130 --> 00:38:47,120
Investigating from the dancer case

766
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:48,580
will only speed things up.

767
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:52,120
Currently, the dancer case is a criminal case,

768
00:38:52,120 --> 00:38:53,510
and it's not under our jurisdiction.

769
00:38:53,510 --> 00:38:56,550
Captain Zhang is already investigating.

770
00:38:56,820 --> 00:38:58,720
If any information about Wang Liqun

771
00:38:58,720 --> 00:38:59,760
is discovered,

772
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,640
he will inform us in time,

773
00:39:02,230 --> 00:39:04,160
so you don't need to worry about it.

774
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:05,520
Alright,

775
00:39:06,330 --> 00:39:08,090
Director, it turns out you're so thoughtful.

776
00:39:08,090 --> 00:39:09,420
We'll follow your plan.

777
00:39:11,830 --> 00:39:15,580
[Arrangement]

778
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:14,590
Tomorrow, we continue the investigation.

779
00:39:14,590 --> 00:39:15,910
I'll emphasize again.

780
00:39:15,940 --> 00:39:18,600
All teams must not leave your posts without permission.

781
00:39:18,600 --> 00:39:20,270
Work in pairs and act together.

782
00:39:20,270 --> 00:39:21,250
Yes.

783
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:25,020
We're going to fail to finish the task again today.

784
00:39:25,380 --> 00:39:26,740
Don't worry.

785
00:39:26,760 --> 00:39:28,840
This time, I guarantee we'll finish the task on time.

786
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:31,070
What time is it? You're still bragging.

787
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:32,790
Listen to me.

788
00:39:32,950 --> 00:39:34,310
We'll act separately.

789
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:35,570
Our speed will double.

790
00:39:36,140 --> 00:39:38,140
But what if the Director finds out?

791
00:39:38,180 --> 00:39:39,700
What's our job?

792
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:41,650
Don't you know how to keep secrets?

793
00:39:43,020 --> 00:39:44,330
Where are you going?

794
00:39:50,810 --> 00:39:52,800
[Shanghai People's Government Public Security Bureau]

795
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:54,670
You're saying

796
00:39:54,690 --> 00:39:56,790
the dead dancer is Zhao Wangju?

797
00:39:56,930 --> 00:39:57,610
Yes.

798
00:39:57,790 --> 00:39:59,230
Look at these two photos.

799
00:39:59,390 --> 00:40:00,790
Both show a distinct birthmark

800
00:40:00,790 --> 00:40:02,140
in the same spot on the wrist.

801
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:04,410
Although the birthmark on the corpse has been destroyed,

802
00:40:04,410 --> 00:40:06,240
the remaining part matches exactly

803
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:08,430
with the one in Zhao Wangju's photo.

804
00:40:09,150 --> 00:40:09,880
Alright,

805
00:40:10,420 --> 00:40:13,280
confirming the victim's identity makes it easier.

806
00:40:13,670 --> 00:40:15,590
Let's immediately check Zhao Wangju's

807
00:40:15,590 --> 00:40:16,520
dancer license.

808
00:40:17,680 --> 00:40:18,280
Let's go.

809
00:40:25,630 --> 00:40:26,180
Hello?

810
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:28,300
The dancer case has been exposed.

811
00:40:28,900 --> 00:40:30,590
Stay away from

812
00:40:30,670 --> 00:40:32,000
the Dai Yueqing matter.

813
00:40:34,470 --> 00:40:36,010
But I've been

814
00:40:36,620 --> 00:40:38,140
tracking this matter.

815
00:40:38,410 --> 00:40:39,880
May I ask

816
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:43,860
if it will be handed over to Xu Wei?

817
00:40:44,090 --> 00:40:47,070
It's all for your safety.

818
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:48,900
Don't be ungrateful.

819
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:51,960
From now on, you'll only handle the Bulbul lead.

820
00:40:52,550 --> 00:40:55,140
Clear out the Putuo points immediately.

821
00:40:55,620 --> 00:40:56,940
Do as I say.

822
00:40:58,620 --> 00:40:59,950
Alright, I understand.

823
00:41:19,940 --> 00:41:21,060
Lin Shaobai,

824
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,670
why are you just coming back?

825
00:41:24,670 --> 00:41:26,180
You scared me half to death.

826
00:41:26,180 --> 00:41:27,350
The meeting is about to start.

827
00:41:27,350 --> 00:41:28,950
We're the only ones missing.

828
00:41:29,300 --> 00:41:30,470
Calm down.

829
00:41:35,270 --> 00:41:35,800
Let's go.

830
00:41:38,940 --> 00:41:41,750
[Arrangement]

831
00:41:43,110 --> 00:41:45,830
Why haven't Lin Shaobai and Cen Xiaoman arrived yet?

832
00:41:45,830 --> 00:41:47,470
Is Lin Shaobai slacking off again?

833
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,550
Doggy.

834
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:52,490
I've noticed you seem to enjoy targeting me.

835
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,310
Who said I'm slacking off?

836
00:41:55,310 --> 00:41:59,110
[Arrangement]

837
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,510
Let me tell you,

838
00:41:56,540 --> 00:41:57,710
today we

839
00:41:57,730 --> 00:41:59,360
investigated 132 households.

840
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:00,550
Everything is recorded.

841
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:02,100
My legs are about to break.

842
00:42:03,120 --> 00:42:04,190
Right, Xiaoman?

843
00:42:04,770 --> 00:42:05,990
Shaobai did well.

844
00:42:06,020 --> 00:42:07,260
He's more than us.

845
00:42:07,310 --> 00:42:08,200
Yes, Xiaoman.

846
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:09,090
