847
00:42:09,090 --> 00:42:10,000
Teach us.

848
00:42:10,190 --> 00:42:11,060
First, let's have the meeting.

849
00:42:11,060 --> 00:42:12,300
We'll tell you after the meeting.

850
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:12,930
Xiaoman,

851
00:42:13,100 --> 00:42:14,830
